import React from "react"
import {ThemeContext} from "./themeContext"
import {Switch, Route} from "react-router-dom"
function Main(){

    return (
        <Switch>
            <Route exact path="/">
                <Home />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/about">
                <About />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/contact">
                <Contact />
            </Route>                       
        </Switch>
    )
}

export default Main
